summary:
Weekly Highlights of September 2nd - 8th:
🌷 I visited the Green Bay Botanical Garden for the first time, after living in Green Bay for three years.  Even though it's later in the season and many of the flowers are past their prime blooming period, it was still quite beautiful.  I can't wait to visit again this winter when they have the Festival of Lights over the holidays...
